page.title: 10HISTORY OF MY FAMILY
page.content: My name is Tracey Blockwell I have lived in Swaffham all my life. l have a grandad living in Swaffham. My grandad used to be in the Swaffham town football team in the 1930's with his brother. My grandad's brother later went into the war, he didn't have to but he thought it would be a change. In the war he caught a disease called Disantry. He died when he was twenty nine years old and his name is on the war memorial and in the parish church. My dad's name is exactly the same as my grandad's brother because my grandad was named him after him.
